x4freetext: THE TARGET MATERIAL IS EVAPORATED IN THE FORM OF A SALT
ONTO A NUMBER OF GRAPHITE STRIPS.TARGETS CONSISTED  OF
1 TO 3 MG/CM**2 OF U-238,TH-232 AND U-235.
/BY COMPILER/.AUTHORS COULD NOT DETECT GROUND AND
ISOMER STATES SEPARATELY.THEREFORE TWO CASES WERE
ISOMER STATES SIMULTANEOUSLY AND ISOMER STATE IS
DECAYING TO GROUND STATE ONLY.SEE FLAG (3.).
2.INDEPENDENT PRODUCTION OF GROUND STATE AND ISOMER
STATE SIMULTANEOUSLY ,BUT ISOMER STATE IS DECAYING
BY ISOMERIC TRANSITION AND BETA ONE.THEREFORE THIS
CROSS SECTION IS MAXIMUM VALUE FOR GROUND STATE
